metacity: metacity (GNOME Window Manager)
metacity:
metacity: Metacity (rhymes with "capacity") is a window manager used by default 
metacity: in the GNOME desktop environment. The development of Metacity 
metacity: was started by Havoc Pennington and it is released under the GNU General 
metacity: Public License.
metacity: 
metacity: Although Metacity is part of the GNOME project and designed to integrate 
metacity: into the GNOME desktop, it does not require GNOME to run, and GNOME can be 
metacity: used with different window managers. 
metacity: 
